title: User query: Plan description from client LLM
log: Create a Wayang plan that finds all the purchases in the household appliances file for purchases made in october 2025. It should only include purchases for organisation which have more than 10 departments, also return the creditor name of these purchases as well as the price and the purchase line. Output in a textfile.

operations.udf: (t: ((Int, Int, String, Double), (Int, String))) => { val p = t._1; val c = t._2; s"${c._2} | ${p._4} | ${p._3}" }

log.thoughts: Count departments per organisation, filter to >10, filter purchases to Oct 2025, then join with creditors to attach names and output the desired fields to a text file.

title: Class: PlanMapper Mapped plan finalized for execution

data.table: (SELECT organisation_id, creditor_id, invoice_date, invoice_line_no, invoice_line_descr, invoice_line_price FROM factpurchases) as X
(SELECT creditor_id, name FROM creditor) as X

data.udf: (t: ((Int, Int, String, Double), (Int, String))) => { val p = t._1; val c = t._2; s"${c._2} | ${p._4} | ${p._3}" }

title: Wayang: Wayang plan sent to Wayang
Err: Wayang error. Plan executed unsucessful
